# C2K autonomous loop

When this rule applies (user asked for hands-off / feature loop / backlog automation, or `.cursor/c2k-loop-active.json` exists):

## Forbidden

- `AskQuestion` — decide locally; document assumptions in BACKLOG_QUEUE Notes or HANDOFF
- `SwitchMode` — implement in Agent mode
- Stopping after one item with only a summary — **continue** to the next `pending` queue row
- New parallel tables/routes when [`docs/EXTEND_BEFORE_ADD.md`](../docs/EXTEND_BEFORE_ADD.md) says extend existing
